61
00:09:29,780 --> 00:09:30,700
Semua sudah di sini.

62
00:09:42,610 --> 00:09:43,370
Kau juga di sini.

63
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:53,490
Halo, Tuan Xu.

64
00:09:53,490 --> 00:09:54,460
Aku adalah kakak iparmu.

65
00:10:04,850 --> 00:10:05,650
Kita bertemu lagi.

66
00:10:07,850 --> 00:10:10,300
Sesama keluarga, biar kubantu kau.

67
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,500
Kau bahkan mewaspadaiku?

68
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:21,530
Aku tahu Zirah Merah Fu.

69
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:24,970
Kalau kukatakan Zirah Merah Fu
tidak berkaitan denganku?

70
00:10:25,010 --> 00:10:25,940
Menurutmu, aku percaya?

71
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:30,060
Aku tidak ikut bertarung.

72
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,010
Semuanya silakan saja.

73
00:10:31,250 --> 00:10:31,730
Tuan Xu.

74
00:10:31,890 --> 00:10:32,420
Silakan.

75
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,980
Kau hanya ingin mengambil hasil?

76
