Benar juga.

81
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:55,650
Tuan Xu.

82
00:10:55,980 --> 00:10:56,610
Kita terkepung.

83
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:57,900
Keadaan tidak menguntungkan.

84
